Reasoning: The paper deals with coded caching schemes and optimization problems related to content placement and delivery in a network with a server and multiple users. This falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), and multimedia (cs.MM).
